TITLE: Verbose Account Query in Casper Network
DESCRIPTION: This command performs a verbose query of account information, providing detailed output including the JSON-RPC request and response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-1.5.X/resources/beginner/querying-network.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
casper-client query-global-state -v \
  --id 4 \
  --node-address https://node.testnet.casper.network \
  --state-root-hash a306a9cf869e52fe9eacdc28aade94215112cc04b6737b3669c35568a47a7dc2 \
  --key 01360af61b50cdcb7b92cffe2c99315d413d34ef77fadee0c105cc4f1d4120f986
```

