TITLE: Creating a Reproducible Casper Project
DESCRIPTION: Creates a Casper project with a rustc wrapper for cross-platform binary reproducibility, which is important for verifying smart contract binaries on the blockchain.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-2.0.0/developers/writing-onchain-code/getting-started.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cargo casper my_project --wrapper
```

