TITLE: Calculating Validator Rewards Formula in Casper 2.0
DESCRIPTION: This mathematical formula calculates the era rewards for a validator in Casper 2.0, consisting of three components: block production rewards, finality signature publication rewards, and finality signature contribution rewards. The formula takes into account validator weight, block production, and signature activities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/condor/validator-rewards.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: mathematical notation
CODE:
```
Era rewards for validator i = 

**** (n in **N***) **i(n)** * (**rR/N**) (block production)

+ **** (n in **N***) **i(n)** * **** (j in **S(n)**) (**w(j)/W**) * (**f(1-r)R/N**) (finality signature publication)  

+ **** (n in **N***) **s_i(n)** * (**w(i)/W**) * (**(1-f)(1-r)R/N**) (finality signature contribution)
```

