DESCRIPTION: This React component uses 'casper-js-sdk' and 'axios' to create an interface for updating a message on the Casper blockchain. It defines an input field and a button to trigger a function that calls the smart contract's "update_message" entrypoint. Required libraries include 'casper-js-sdk', 'axios', and 'react'.
