TITLE: Generating Keys with OpenSSL
DESCRIPTION: Commands to generate Ed25519 keys using OpenSSL cryptography toolkit on Linux.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-2.0.0/concepts/accounts-and-keys.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
openssl genpkey -algorithm ed25519 -out secret_key.pem

{ echo -n 01; openssl pkey -outform DER -pubout -in "secret_key.pem" | tail -c +13 | openssl base64 | openssl base64 -d | hexdump -ve '/1 "%02x" ' | tr -d "/n"; } > public_key_hex
```

