TITLE: Defining "info_get_reward" RPC Endpoint in JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON structure defines the "info_get_reward" RPC endpoint, which returns reward information for a validator or delegator for a specified era. It requires a public key for a validator and can optionally accept an era identifier and a delegator's public key. This RPC call returns an object containing details such as the API version, era ID, reward amount, and delegation rate. The JSON schema ensures proper request and response validation.
