SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/docs/resources/beginner/counter-testnet/walkthrough.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
casper-client account-address --public-key [PATH_TO_PUBLIC_KEY]
```

