TITLE: Setting URef Access Rights - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Code examples demonstrating how to create URefs with different access rights combinations using the with_access_rights method. Shows all possible access right combinations from NONE to READ_ADD_WRITE.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/docs/developers/dapps/uref-security.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
