LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { DeployUtil, CLPublicKey } from 'casper-js-sdk';

const signedDeploy = DeployUtil.setSignature(
  deploy,
  signatureRS,
  CLPublicKey.fromHex(accountPublicKey)
);
```

