TITLE: Example: Withdrawing Bid via Compiled Wasm on Testnet (Bash)
DESCRIPTION: An example `casper-client` command demonstrating how to unbond stake (withdraw 1000 CSPR) on the Casper Testnet by deploying the `withdraw_bid.wasm` contract. It specifies the path to the compiled Wasm, the validator's public key, the amount to withdraw, and sets a payment amount of 4 CSPR.
