TITLE: Executing Redelegate Transaction in Casper Network
DESCRIPTION: This command allows a user to redelegate their previously staked CSPR to a new validator. It requires the delegator's public key, old and new validator's public keys, redelegation amount, gas price tolerance, and either a secret key or initiator address.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/docs/concepts/transactions.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
