TITLE: Representing the Era Rewards Formula for Validators in Casper 2.0
DESCRIPTION: A mathematical formula that calculates validator rewards in Casper 2.0, consisting of three components: rewards for block production, finality signature publication, and finality signature contribution. The formula uses weighted calculations based on validator stake and participation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/src/pages/condor/validator-rewards.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
Era rewards for validator i = 

**** (n in **N***) **i(n)** * (**rR/N**) (block production)

&#43; **** (n in **N***) **i(n)** * **** (j in **S(n)**) (**w(j)/W**) * (**f(1-r)R/N**) (finality signature publication)  

&#43; **** (n in **N***) **s_i(n)** * (**w(i)/W**) * (**(1-f)(1-r)R/N**) (finality signature contribution)
```

