TITLE: Creating Session Parameter for Stored Contract Call in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates the `session` part of a deploy, specifying a call to a stored contract by its hash (the auction manager contract). It requires the auction manager contract hash (decoded from Base16), the contract entry point (`delegate`, `undelegate`, or `redelegate`), and the previously defined runtime arguments (`args`). Depends on `decodeBase16` and `DeployUtil` from `casper-js-sdk`.
