TITLE: Loading Secret Key from File - Python - python
DESCRIPTION: Uses pycspr to read a PEM-format private key and construct a Keypair object, using ED25519 algorithm. The path to the private key file must be provided and the file must be readable. Replace ED25519 with SECP256K1 if another key type is needed. Output: keypair object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-2.0.0/developers/dapps/sdk/client-library-usage.md#2025-04-22_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
import pycspr
keypair = pycspr.parse_private_key(
    "./secret_key.pem",
    pycspr.crypto.KeyAlgorithm.ED25519
)
```

