TITLE: Defining JSON Schema for Validator Changes
DESCRIPTION: Describes the JSON schema for the "info_get_validator_changes" RPC. This RPC returns the status changes of validators on the network. The schema requires an API version and an array of validator status changes. Validators changes include fields such as public key and status changes, which are detailed in JsonValidatorChanges.
