LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
```rust
pub enum Tag {
    Deploy,
    FinalizedApprovals,
    Block,
    GossipedAddress,
    BlockAndMetadataByHeight,
    BlockHeaderByHash,
    BlockHeaderAndFinalitySignaturesByHeight,
    TrieOrChunk,
    BlockAndDeploysByHash,
    BlockHeaderBatch,
    FinalitySignaturesByHash,
}
```
```

