TITLE: Casper Wallet Provider Implementation
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript implementation for getting the Casper Wallet provider instance with timeout configuration
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-1.5.X/developers/dapps/template-frontend.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const REQUESTS_TIMEOUT_MS = 30 * 60 * 1000;

export const getProvider = () => {
    let providerConstructor = window.CasperWalletProvider;
    if (providerConstructor === undefined) {
        alert("Casper Wallet extension is not installed!");
        return;
    }
    let provider = providerConstructor({
        timeout: REQUESTS_TIMEOUT_MS
    });
    return provider;
}
```

