TITLE: Retrieving Block Transfers with chain_get_block_transfers in JSON-RPC
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the chain_get_block_transfers method to get all successful native transfers within a specific block on the Casper network. It includes the request format with a block identifier parameter and demonstrates the expected response structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-2.0.0/developers/json-rpc/json-rpc-informational.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
