TITLE: Enabling Contract on Casper Network via CLI
DESCRIPTION: Enables a specified contract on the Casper network by deploying changes using Casper client. It requires contract package and contract hashes, admin's secret key, and session path.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-2.0.0/operators/setup-network/create-private.md#2025-04-22_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
casper-client \
  put-deploy \
  -n $NODE_ADDR \
  --chain-name $CHAIN_NAME \
  --secret-key admin/secret_key.pem \
  --session-account=$(<alice/public_key_hex) \
  --session-path enable_contract.wasm \
  --payment-amount 3000000000 \
  --session-arg "contract_package_hash:account_hash='account-hash-$CONTRACT_PACKAGE_HASH'" \
  --session-arg "contract_hash:account_hash='account-hash-$CONTRACT_HASH'"
```

