TITLE: Calculating Round Issuance Rate in Casper Network
DESCRIPTION: Formula for computing the round issuance rate based on the annual issuance rate, adjusted for the minimum round length. This rate determines how many tokens are issued per round.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/docs/concepts/economics/consensus.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
round_issuance_rate = (1 + issuance_rate)^(2^minimum_round_exponent / ticks_per_year) - 1
```

