TITLE: Preparing a Deploy to Add Default Account as an Associated Key in Rust
DESCRIPTION: This Rust code snippet constructs a `DeployItem` intended to add the `DEFAULT_ACCOUNT_ADDR` as an associated key to the account identified by `account_addr_1`. It uses the `ADD_KEYS_WASM` session code, specifies `DEFAULT_ACCOUNT_ADDR` as the `ASSOCIATED_ACCOUNT` argument, sets the payment, uses `account_addr_1` as the sole authorization key, and targets `account_addr_1`'s address. Note: This snippet only builds the deploy item; execution is handled later.
