TITLE: Defining Contract and Global State Related Schemas in JSON
DESCRIPTION: JSON schema definitions for Casper Network API components including ContractHash, DisabledVersion, Groups, ContractPackageStatus, and GlobalStateIdentifier. These schemas define the structure and validation rules for contract-related data in the Casper Network.
