TITLE: Calculating Round Seigniorage Rate using Python Fraction
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the Python code used to calculate the `round_seigniorage_rate` as a fraction, representing the annual issuance rate (8%) adjusted for minimum block time (2^15 ms) relative to a year. This calculation utilizes the `Fraction` class to maintain precision and limits the denominator for representation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-1.5.X/operators/setup-network/chain-spec.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
Fraction((1 + 0.08)**((2**15)/31536000000) - 1).limit_denominator(1000000000)
```

