TITLE: Undelegating Tokens via Compiled WASM
DESCRIPTION: Alternative method to undelegate tokens using compiled WASM. This method requires building casper-node contracts and costs more (around 6 CSPR) compared to the system auction contract method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-1.5.X/developers/cli/undelegate.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
casper-client put-deploy \
--node-address <HOST:PORT> \
--secret-key <PATH> \
--chain-name <CHAIN_NAME> \
--payment-amount <PAYMENT_AMOUNT_IN_MOTES> \
--session-path <PATH_TO_WASM>/undelegate.wasm \
--session-arg "validator:public_key='<HEX_ENCODED_VALIDATOR_PULIC_KEY>'" \
--session-arg "amount:u512='<AMOUNT_TO_UNDELEGATE>'" \
--session-arg "delegator:public_key='<HEX_ENCODED_DELEGATOR_PULIC_KEY>'"
```

