TITLE: Defining Transaction Schema in JSON
DESCRIPTION: JSON schema definition for Transaction, which is a versioned wrapper for a deploy or transaction. It includes definitions for Deploy and TransactionV1 types, representing different versions of transactions in the Casper Network.
