TITLE: Computing Round Issuance Rate for Casper Network
DESCRIPTION: Formula for calculating the round issuance rate, which is the annual issuance rate adjusted to a single consensus round. This value is used in the reward calculation mechanism.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casper-network/docs-redux/blob/dev/versioned_docs/version-1.5.X/concepts/economics/consensus.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
round_issuance_rate = (1 + issuance_rate)^(2^minimum_round_exponent / ticks_per_year) - 1
```

